OL,3,CPostcard arrives at Welsh address 121
OL,4,Cyears after it was sent
OL,6,FA postcard has been delivered to an
OL,7,Faddress in Wales 121 years after it
OL,8,Fwas sent.
OL,10,FStaff at Swansea Building Society
OL,11,Fcouldn't believe their eyes when going
OL,12,Fthrough the mail at their Cradock
OL,13,FStreet head office on Friday, 16
OL,14,FAugust.
OL,16,FAlongside the usual mortgage and
OL,17,Fsavings-related letters appeared a
OL,18,Fpostcard, which dropped out from the
OL,19,Fmiddle of the pile with a King Edward
OL,20,FVII stamp on it, dated 3 August, 1903.
