OL,3,CPostcard arrives at Welsh address 121
OL,4,Cyears after it was sent
OL,6,FIt was written for a woman named Lydia
OL,7,FDavies, who presumably lived there at
OL,8,Fthe time there were houses at the
OL,9,Faddress, instead of the bank.
OL,11,FHenry Darby, marketing and
OL,12,Fcommunications officer at Swansea
OL,13,FBuilding Society, said: "It turned up
OL,14,Fcompletely out of the blue on Friday.
OL,16,F"The postman came to the door as
OL,17,Fnormal with lots of letters regarding
OL,18,Fmortgages and savings and stuff for
OL,19,Four team to process.
