OL,6,F"As one of the managers was going
OL,7,Fthrough it, a postcard dropped onto
OL,8,Fthe table, not in an envelope, not
OL,9,Fwith a note, just as it was."
OL,11,FMr Darby said: "The address is
OL,12,Fcorrect, we are still 11 (and 12)
OL,13,FCradock Street, but it's 121 years
OL,14,Flater than expected. It's wild,
OL,15,Factually. A little bit spooky.
