OL,6,FThe main body of the postcard says:
OL,7,F"Dear L. I could not, it was
OL,8,Fimpossible to get the pair of these. I
OL,9,Fam so sorry, but I hope you are
OL,10,Fenjoying yourself at home. I have got
OL,11,Fnow about 10 (unreadable) pocket money
OL,12,Fnot counting the train fare so I'm
OL,13,Fdoing alright."
OL,15,FThe bank has put an appeal out on
OL,16,Fsocial media asking for anyone with
OL,17,Finformation on Ms Davies, or anything
OL,18,Felse to help shed light on the
OL,19,Fmystery, to come forward and get in
OL,20,Ftouch via their social media channels.
