OL,4,Cyears after it was sent
OL,6,FMr Darby said: "We know it's quite
OL,7,Flong ago, but we thought it would be
OL,8,Fso fascinating to know what was life
OL,9,Flike on Cradock Street 121 years ago.
OL,11,F"The building society itself was set
OL,12,Fup 20 years after the postcard was
OL,13,Fsent. From what we could gauge looking
OL,14,Fat the archives, we think there were
OL,15,Fmore traditional houses in this place
OL,16,Fwhich were bombed, and our office is a
OL,17,Frebuild but the address has stayed the
OL,18,Fsame.
