OL,6,F"Opposite, the Albert Hall was open at
OL,7,Fthe time in the 1860s, when Oscar
OL,8,FWilde performed, so Lydia was probably
OL,9,Fwalking across the road to see those
OL,10,Fpeople who performed there."
OL,12,FA Royal Mail spokeswoman said: "It is
OL,13,Flikely that this postcard was put back
OL,14,Finto our system rather than being lost
OL,15,Fin the post for over a century. When
OL,16,Fan item is in our system, we are under
OL,17,Fobligation to deliver it to the
OL,18,Fcorrect address."
